  "subject": "[CCSDK] Tweak job ccsdk/oran/merge-verify jenkins job for incomplete deployments",
  "commit_message": "[CCSDK] Tweak job ccsdk/oran/merge-verify jenkins job for incomplete deployments\n\nRef: https://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/ci-management/+/142741\nAdd setting for maven-deploy-plugin to stop build from failing if a module whose packaging\ntype is not 'pom' does not deploy artifacts.  This is valid in the case of projects with\npackaging type 'feature', which create artifacts that the deploy artifact does not consider\nattachments.\n\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-4143\nChange-Id: I2986322c1f6fb1848c62cd09eaceb27d103f4ea3\nSigned-off-by: JohnKeeney <john.keeney@est.tech>\n",
